reviews.review_text: Mother Nature's show People listening already know to look for this show, so not much needs to be said for the playing. However this is an incredible sounding remaster of this already fantastic AUD. One of the absolute clearest I've ever heard. Audience reactions are what make this show what it is and being able to hear every concertgoer and the band just as clear as the other almost makes this feel more realistic than any matrix
